AI Ethics The core values of Salesforce: Trust, Customer Success, Innovation, Equality, Sustainability. Quote Kasparov :&ldquo;A good human and a machine is the best combination.&rdquo;
Types of Bias Measurement or Dataset Bias Can be introduced when a person makes a mistake labeling the data or through machine error. A characteristic or factor can be over-or-underrepresented in your dataset.
Type 1 vs Type 2 Error Type 1 - false positive, predicts positive result but is actually negative; Type 2 - false negative, predicts negative result but is actually positive;
